{"lastModified":1772813452948,"uri":"c::7818345123::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nEl Marita, is a lovely Lagoon 46 that can accommodates up to 8 guests in 4 cabins,  plus two extra cabins for the crew.  All cabins  have double beds and their own ensuite facilieties. El Marita has 3 fridges and an extra sink in the cockpit. She is fully air conditioned , equipped with a generator and 5 air conditioning units. El Marita was built in 2021 and had an upgrade in 2024 as follows:\nNew Teak in cockpit and flybridge\nNew wooden table in Cockpit\nLed lights installed in flybridge\nNew chairs in cockpit\nNew carpet in interior of the yacht\n\nWatertoys/Amenities:\n2 Sescooters Jobe Pro Infinity (new 2025)\n2 SUPs ( Stand up Paddles)\n1 double seater canoe\n1 blast for children \nSnorkelling equipment for 8 guests \nFishing equipment\nUnderwater lights\nHiFi Fusion for music easily connected to Bluetooth \nWiFi \n\nEl Marita is available from Lefkas Ionian.","blueprint":{"name":"EL MARITA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1876d490-ea0d-11ef-b5d1-370650e66f3a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ebdb7fc0-ea0d-11ef-8867-7b8c79837c85/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ebe60710-ea0d-11ef-8867-7b8c79837c85/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ebcab6e0-ea0d-11ef-8867-7b8c79837c85/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ebeb8550-ea0d-11ef-8867-7b8c79837c85/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ebade010-ea0d-11ef-8867-7b8c79837c85/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca408-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ebcb5320-ea0d-11ef-8867-7b8c7983